br />\n跟住佢又話,你真係以為唔驚我打你,依家你係老豆定我係老豆<br />\n我又同佢講,你咪a你,我報警tim a<br />\n跟住佢冇出聲<br />\n痴線"},{"pid":"0742e909642b00f5ad90d288e1e43cceba50c999","tid":95600,"uid":69064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:33:35.000Z","msg":"搵我 我陪你食"},{"pid":"fc21a949d017981f484d67e9ecfda7e3eb56d0ca","tid":95600,"uid":50218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:38:28.000Z","msg":"sorly lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18cb4bfd24d1afeec40e873acbb2e438b98a8d1","tid":95600,"uid":11913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:40:32.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"763a52c3602204771210507ff8882c777fbd67cd","tid":95600,"uid":15370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:56:31.000Z","msg":"樓豬呢鋪我就撐你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}